title: SAMSUNG Galaxy Buds Fan Edition(FE) SM-R400, Active Noise-Cancelling, Wireless Bluetooth v5.2 Earbuds, Android 8.0 and Up - (Graphite)
description: Hear what you want, not what you don’t Galaxy Buds FE feature Active Noise Cancellation to help minimize the distracting sounds in your environment, from idle chatter to an airplane flying overhead. Designed for comfort. Shaped to fit. Easily control with a tap Easily control with a tap Clearly defined areas for tapping and gripping look and feel different, making it easy to secure your Buds, pause the audio and change the volume with a simple tap. Audio that switches automatically With Auto Switch, Galaxy Buds FE connect to whatever device you are on so you don’t miss a beat. Audio that switches automatically Pairs easily with your Galaxy Pairs easily with your Galaxy devices Galaxy Buds FE pair easily to your other Galaxy devices — just tap to connect as soon as you open the case.
